OL,3,CCouncils in England face funding gap
OL,4,Cof #6.2bn, says report
OL,6,FCouncils in England face a funding gap
OL,7,Fof #6.2 billion over the next few
OL,8,Fyears, according to a report.
OL,10,FA study by the Local Government
OL,11,FAssociation (LGA) showed that the
OL,12,Fproblem is being driven by rising
OL,13,Fcosts and demands to provide adult
OL,14,Fsocial care, children's services,
OL,15,Fhomelessness support and transport for
OL,16,Fchildren with special needs and
OL,17,Fdisabilities.
