OL,3,CCouncils in England face funding gap
OL,4,Cof #6.2bn, says report
OL,6,FThe LGA said a new relationship
OL,7,Fbetween central and local government,
OL,8,Fproviding long-term financial
OL,9,Fcertainty, is the only way for the
OL,10,Fnext government to solve such issues.
OL,12,FCouncils are increasingly left with
OL,13,Fless funding to provide universal
OL,14,Flocal services that people rely on
OL,15,Fevery day such as keeping streets
OL,16,Fclean, filling potholes and tackling
OL,17,Fanti-social behaviour, said the
OL,18,Fassociation.
