OL,3,CCouncils in England face funding gap
OL,4,Cof #6.2bn, says report
OL,6,FA recent LGA survey found two-thirds
OL,7,Fof councils had already had to make
OL,8,Fcutbacks to neighbourhood services
OL,9,Fthis year including waste collections,
OL,10,Froad repairs and library and leisure
OL,11,Fservices as they struggle to plug
OL,12,Ffunding gaps.
OL,14,FThe LGA is calling on all political
OL,15,Fparties to commit to a "significant
OL,16,Fand sustained" increase in funding for
OL,17,Fcouncils in the next Spending Review,
OL,18,Falongside multi-year funding
OL,19,Fsettlements for councils and plans to
OL,20,Freform the local government finance
OL,21,Fsystem.
