OL,3,CCouncils in England face funding gap
OL,4,Cof #6.2bn, says report
OL,6,FWithout this, the LGA said, cost and
OL,7,Fdemand pressures will continue to
OL,8,Fstretch council budgets "to the limit"
OL,9,Fin the coming years, leaving more
OL,10,Fcouncils unable to deliver their legal
OL,11,Fduties for their residents and putting
OL,12,Fvital services at further risk of
OL,13,Fcutbacks.
OL,15,FKevin Bentley, senior vice chairman of
OL,16,Fthe LGA, said: "We all rely on local
OL,17,Fgovernment to keep our streets clean,
OL,18,Fcollect our bins, fix our potholes,
OL,19,Fbuild more homes, create jobs, keep
OL,20,Fchildren safe and support people of
OL,21,Fall ages to live fulfilling lives.
