OL,3,CCouncils in England face funding gap
OL,4,Cof #6.2bn, says report
OL,6,F"However, a funding gap facing local
OL,7,Fservices of more than #6 billion over
OL,8,Fthe next two years ` fuelled by rising
OL,9,Fcost and demand pressures ` means a
OL,10,Fchasm will continue to grow between
OL,11,Fwhat people and their communities need
OL,12,Fand want from their councils and what
OL,13,Fcouncils can deliver.
OL,15,F"On July 5, the next government will
OL,16,Fbe faced with many challenges, whether
OL,17,Fit is building more affordable
OL,18,Fhousing, improving care for adults and
OL,19,Fchildren, reducing homelessness,
OL,20,Fboosting inclusive growth or tackling
OL,21,Fclimate change.
