OL,3,CCouncils in England face funding gap
OL,4,Cof #6.2bn, says report
OL,6,F"Local government's offer to the next
OL,7,Fgovernment is huge. Respect us, trust
OL,8,Fus and fund us. By working together as
OL,9,Fequal partners, we can meet the
OL,10,Ffundamental long-term challenges
OL,11,Ffacing our communities."
OL,13,FUnite national officer Clare Keogh
OL,14,Fsaid: "Local government has been
OL,15,Fdecimated over the last 14 years, with
OL,16,Fthousands of frontline jobs already
OL,17,Fcut, while demand for services keeps
OL,18,Frising.
