OL,3,CCouncils in England face funding gap
OL,4,Cof #6.2bn, says report
OL,6,F"Services are already stretched far
OL,7,Ftoo thin. The situation is at breaking
OL,8,Fpoint and further job losses cannot be
OL,9,Fthe answer.
OL,11,F"The incoming government must commit
OL,12,Fto properly and fairly funding the
OL,13,Fsector to meet need, and to reverse
OL,14,Fthe years of decline we have seen."
OL,16,FUnison's head of local government Mike
OL,17,FShort said: "Councils are facing an
OL,18,Fexistential crisis because of years of
OL,19,Fsevere government underfunding.
