OL,3,CCouncils in England face funding gap
OL,4,Cof #6.2bn, says report
OL,6,F"Wave after wave of budget cuts to
OL,7,Fessential services has harmed
OL,8,Fcommunities immensely, with the worst
OL,9,Foff always the hardest hit.
OL,11,F"Authorities have been forced to sell
OL,12,Foff buildings, open spaces and other
OL,13,Fprized assets, and cut thousands of
OL,14,Fjobs.
OL,16,F"But still their books won't balance `
OL,17,Fand now scores of town halls face
OL,18,Feffective bankruptcy.
