OL,3,CCouncils in England face funding gap
OL,4,Cof #6.2bn, says report
OL,6,F"Without a sustained programme of
OL,7,Fproper investment many more will go
OL,8,Funder. This cannot be allowed to
OL,9,Fhappen. Local services, and the
OL,10,Fcouncils that provide them, are too
OL,11,Fimportant to lose."
OL,13,FSharon Wilde, GMB national officer,
OL,14,Fsaid: "This report is welcome ` it
OL,15,Fhighlights what GMB has been saying
OL,16,Ffor more than a decade. Our vital
OL,17,Fpublic services are being starved of
OL,18,Fthe funding they need to operate.
