OL,3,CCouncils in England face funding gap
OL,4,Cof #6.2bn, says report
OL,6,F"It must serve as a wake-up call to
OL,7,Fthe next government, who will need to
OL,8,Fget to grips with the perilous state
OL,9,Fof social care across our country.
OL,11,F"We are hearing devastating stories
OL,12,Ffrom people impacted by this chronic
OL,13,Funderfunding with many families being
OL,14,Fleft to plug the gap of vital support
OL,15,Ftheir loved ones need.
OL,17,F"We also know many people are having
OL,18,Ftheir funding drastically cut despite
OL,19,Ftheir needs staying the same."
